ll, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013024, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace and Allah’s mercy and blessings be upon you, O leaders to the true guidance. I entrust you with Allah and send salutations to you. We believe in Allah and in the Messenger and in that which you have conveyed and that to which you have guided. O Allah, then write us down among those who bear witness.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aap sab par salaam ho ay hidaayat ke Aimma (a.s) aur Uski rehmat ho aur Uski barkate’n. Aap ko wida karta hu aur Khuda ke supurd (hawaale) karta hu aur aap par salaam bhejta hu, imaan rakhta hu Khuda aur uske Rasool par aur jo aap laaye aur jis ki taraf aap ne rehnumaayi farmaayi. Ay Ma’bood! Hamein yeh gawahi dene waalo’n mein likh de.", "Urdu": "آپ سب پر سلام ہو اے ہدایت کے ائمہ ؑاور اس کی رحمت ہو اور اس کی برکتیں آپ کو وداع کرتا ہوں اورسپردِخدا کرتا ہوں اور آپ پر سلام بھیجتا ہوں ایمان رکھتا ہوں خدا اور اس کے رسولؐ پر اور جو آپ لائے اور جس کی طرف آپ نے رہنمائی فرمائی اے معبود! ہمیں یہ گواہی دینے والوں میں لکھ دے۔", "RArabic": "ASSALAAMO A’LAIKA AIMMA-TAL HODAA WA RAHMA-TULLAA-HE WA BARA-KAATO-HU AS-TAWDE-O’KO-MUL LAAHA WA AQRA-O A’LAIKO-MUS SALAAMO AAMAN-NAA BILLAAHE WA BIR-RASOOLE WA BE-MAA JE-TUM BEHI WA DALAL-TUM A’LAI-HE. ALLAAHUMMA FAK-TUBNAA MA-A’SH SHAAHE-DEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكُمْ اَئِمَّةَ الْهُدٰى وَرَحْمَةُ اللهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهٗ اَسْتَوْدِعُكُمُ اللهَ وَاَقْرَاُ عَلَيْكُمُ السَّلَامُ آمَنَّا بِاللهِ وَبِالرَّسُوْلِ وَبِمَا جِئْتُمْ بِهٖ وَدَلَلْتُمْ عَلَيْهِ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ فَاكْتُبْنَا مَعَ الشَّاهِدِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9